On this scale, this upload is about 5/10.

This attempt to rip off Star Wars was prone to cancellation and became its own cult hit.  Well, the 1978 one more than the 1980 one.
The 1978 movie is included, even though the premiere of the show is basically the same content. The 1979 and 1981 movies are not included for being nothing but rearrangements of episodes from the shows.

These copies are drawn from the highest quality sources possible, but they are encoded with lower bitrates at 360p resolution to make them ideal for the small screen - phones, tablets, laptops, and monitors.
Keep seeding so I can focus on seeding the next upload!
